cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with 3D vision and photometric bundle adjustment, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses optimization techniques and speed-ups, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper mentions the integration of the proposed method with a SLAM algorithm, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
